  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a wok or large frying pan over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and sauté until they start to pop, about 30 seconds.",
    "Chop the onion and squash into small cubes. Add them to the pan with the garlic and cook for 5 minutes on low-medium heat.",
    "Mix in molasses and turmeric powder. Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add salt to taste and stir well to incorporate all ingredients evenly.",
    "Serve hot as a side dish or main course."
